		h4 ABOUT AMIÒ
		p AMIÒ is a luxury  and resort label reflecting a sense of iconic sophistication and elegance, focusing on high quality materials and the perfect fit.
		p Produced and hand-sewn in Los Angeles, AMIÒ is composed of rare and high-quality fabrics sourced from France, Italy, and Germany.

	img.about-description__image_2.box(src="img/about/about-desc-2.jpg" alt="Amio" data-speed="10" data-margin="400")

	.about-description__text.about-description__text_2
		p The collection is a stylized balance of high fashion and global luxury, which embody the core aesthetic of AMIÒ. Founder and designer, Samantha Khoury, draws upon her avant-garde design inspiration from her training in the Fine Arts, passion for haute couture, and multicultural heritage. The introductory 2016/2017 collection features classic silhouettes that embrace the natural curvature of the female form. Inviting earth tones and timeless shades make up the premier color palette.
		p Samantha’s personal belief and passion around social responsibility led her to dedicate part of AMIÒ’s proceeds to supporting the knowledge and education of select humanitarian programs. The Thirst Project is part of many hopeful partnerships, where global commerce helps provide local communities access to clean drinking water and raise awareness about our world’s most valuable resource.

